  "name": "design-a-robust-fix-for-dead-20260414-0414",
  "idea": "Design a robust fix for dead time / frozen tail at the end of video clips in the editor. The plan should: (1) explain where overhang comes from when a clip's timeline span exceeds its playable media span, (2) prevent accidental overhang by default on shot drop and switch-to-final-video, (3) add a clear visual distinction in the timeline when a media clip still has overhang, and (4) provide an explicit user action such as trim-to-media-end or convert tail to intentional hold/freeze behavior instead of accidental dead space.",
